{"word":"салон","level":"B1","ru":"салон","en":"interior","de":"der Innenraum","it":"l'abitacolo","es_ar":"el interior","fr":"l'habitacle","examples":[{"uk":"У салоні автомобіля пахне новою шкірою.","ru":"В салоне автомобиля пахнет новой кожей.","en":"The car's interior smells of new leather.","de":"Der Innenraum des Autos riecht nach neuem Leder.","it":"L'abitacolo dell'auto profuma di pelle nuova.","es_ar":"El interior del auto huele a cuero nuevo.","fr":"L'habitacle de la voiture sent le cuir neuf."}],"topics":["travel-transport"]},
{"word":"досягати","level":"B1","ru":"достигать","en":"to achieve","de":"erreichen","it":"raggiungere","es_ar":"lograr","fr":"atteindre","examples":[{"uk":"Наполеглива праця допомогла їй досягати поставлених цілей.","ru":"Упорный труд помог ей достигать поставленных целей.","en":"Hard work helped her achieve her goals.","de":"Harte Arbeit half ihr, ihre Ziele zu erreichen.","it":"Il duro lavoro l'ha aiutata a raggiungere i suoi obiettivi.","es_ar":"El trabajo duro la ayudó a lograr sus objetivos.","fr":"Le travail acharné l'a aidée à atteindre ses objectifs."}],"syn":["досягти"],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"розвивати","level":"B1","ru":"развивать","en":"to develop","de":"entwickeln","it":"sviluppare","es_ar":"desarrollar","fr":"développer","examples":[{"uk":"Читання допомагає розвивати уяву та словниковий запас.","ru":"Чтение помогает развивать воображение и словарный запас.","en":"Reading helps develop imagination and vocabulary.","de":"Lesen hilft, die Vorstellungskraft und den Wortschatz zu entwickeln.","it":"La lettura aiuta a sviluppare l'immaginazione e il vocabolario.","es_ar":"La lectura ayuda a desarrollar la imaginación y el vocabulario.","fr":"La lecture aide à développer l'imagination et le vocabulaire."}],"syn":["розвинути"],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"покращувати","level":"B1","ru":"улучшать","en":"to improve","de":"verbessern","it":"migliorare","es_ar":"mejorar","fr":"améliorer","examples":[{"uk":"Щоденна практика допомагає покращувати вимову.","ru":"Ежедневная практика помогает улучшать произношение.","en":"Daily practice helps improve pronunciation.","de":"Tägliche Übung hilft, die Aussprache zu verbessern.","it":"La pratica quotidiana aiuta a migliorare la pronuncia.","es_ar":"La práctica diaria ayuda a mejorar la pronunciación.","fr":"La pratique quotidienne aide à améliorer la prononciation."}],"syn":["покращити"],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"уникати","level":"B1","ru":"избегать","en":"to avoid","de":"vermeiden","it":"evitare","es_ar":"evitar","fr":"éviter","examples":[{"uk":"Лікарі радять уникати жирної їжі перед сном.","ru":"Врачи советуют избегать жирной пищи перед сном.","en":"Doctors advise avoiding fatty food before bed.","de":"Ärzte raten, fettiges Essen vor dem Schlafengehen zu vermeiden.","it":"I medici consigliano di evitare cibi grassi prima di dormire.","es_ar":"Los médicos aconsejan evitar la comida grasa antes de dormir.","fr":"Les médecins conseillent d'éviter les aliments gras avant de dormir."}],"syn":["уникнути"],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"вимагати","level":"B1","ru":"требовать","en":"to require","de":"erfordern","it":"richiedere","es_ar":"requerir","fr":"exiger","examples":[{"uk":"Ця робота вимагає багато терпіння й уваги.","ru":"Эта работа требует много терпения и внимания.","en":"This job requires a lot of patience and attention.","de":"Diese Arbeit erfordert viel Geduld und Aufmerksamkeit.","it":"Questo lavoro richiede molta pazienza e attenzione.","es_ar":"Este trabajo requiere mucha paciencia y atención.","fr":"Ce travail exige beaucoup de patience et d'attention."}],"syn":["вимогти"],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"описувати","level":"B1","ru":"описывать","en":"to describe","de":"beschreiben","it":"descrivere","es_ar":"describir","fr":"décrire","examples":[{"uk":"У листі вона описує своє нове місто дуже детально.","ru":"В письме она описывает свой новый город очень подробно.","en":"In the letter she describes her new city in great detail.","de":"Im Brief beschreibt sie ihre neue Stadt sehr ausführlich.","it":"Nella lettera descrive la sua nuova città in modo molto dettagliato.","es_ar":"En la carta describe su nueva ciudad con mucho detalle.","fr":"Dans la lettre, elle décrit sa nouvelle ville en détail."}],"syn":["описати"],"topics":["language-words"]},
{"word":"збільшувати","level":"B1","ru":"увеличивать","en":"to increase","de":"erhöhen","it":"aumentare","es_ar":"aumentar","fr":"augmenter","examples":[{"uk":"Компанія планує збільшувати виробництво наступного року.","ru":"Компания планирует увеличивать производство в следующем году.","en":"The company plans to increase production next year.","de":"Das Unternehmen plant, die Produktion nächstes Jahr zu erhöhen.","it":"L'azienda prevede di aumentare la produzione l'anno prossimo.","es_ar":"La empresa planea aumentar la producción el próximo año.","fr":"L'entreprise prévoit d'augmenter la production l'année prochaine."}],"syn":["збільшити"],"topics":["abstract-ideas","numbers-quantity"]},
{"word":"визнавати","level":"B1","ru":"признавать","en":"to admit","de":"zugeben","it":"ammettere","es_ar":"admitir","fr":"admettre","examples":[{"uk":"Йому важко визнавати свої помилки перед іншими.","ru":"Ему трудно признавать свои ошибки перед другими.","en":"It is hard for him to admit his mistakes in front of others.","de":"Es fällt ihm schwer, seine Fehler vor anderen zuzugeben.","it":"Per lui è difficile ammettere i propri errori davanti agli altri.","es_ar":"Le cuesta admitir sus errores delante de los demás.","fr":"Il lui est difficile d'admettre ses erreurs devant les autres."}],"syn":["визнати"],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"доводити","level":"B1","ru":"доказывать","en":"to prove","de":"beweisen","it":"dimostrare","es_ar":"demostrar","fr":"prouver","examples":[{"uk":"Науковці мають доводити свої теорії за допомогою фактів.","ru":"Учёные должны доказывать свои теории с помощью фактов.","en":"Scientists must prove their theories with facts.","de":"Wissenschaftler müssen ihre Theorien mit Fakten beweisen.","it":"Gli scienziati devono dimostrare le loro teorie con i fatti.","es_ar":"Los científicos deben demostrar sus teorías con hechos.","fr":"Les scientifiques doivent prouver leurs théories avec des faits."}],"syn":["довести"],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"запроваджувати","level":"B1","ru":"вводить","en":"to introduce","de":"einführen","it":"introdurre","es_ar":"introducir","fr":"introduire","examples":[{"uk":"Уряд планує запроваджувати нові правила з наступного року.","ru":"Правительство планирует вводить новые правила со следующего года.","en":"The government plans to introduce new rules from next year.","de":"Die Regierung plant, ab nächstem Jahr neue Regeln einzuführen.","it":"Il governo prevede di introdurre nuove regole a partire dall'anno prossimo.","es_ar":"El gobierno planea introducir nuevas reglas a partir del próximo año.","fr":"Le gouvernement prévoit d'introduire de nouvelles règles à partir de l'année prochaine."}],"syn":["впроваджувати"],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"обґрунтовувати","level":"B1","ru":"обосновывать","en":"to justify","de":"begründen","it":"giustificare","es_ar":"justificar","fr":"justifier","examples":[{"uk":"На екзамені треба обґрунтовувати свою відповідь прикладами.","ru":"На экзамене нужно обосновывать свой ответ примерами.","en":"In the exam you have to justify your answer with examples.","de":"In der Prüfung muss man seine Antwort mit Beispielen begründen.","it":"All'esame bisogna giustificare la propria risposta con esempi.","es_ar":"En el examen hay que justificar la respuesta con ejemplos.","fr":"À l'examen, il faut justifier sa réponse avec des exemples."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"здійснювати","level":"B1","ru":"осуществлять","en":"to carry out","de":"durchführen","it":"realizzare","es_ar":"llevar a cabo","fr":"réaliser","examples":[{"uk":"Компанія почала здійснювати сміливий план розвитку.","ru":"Компания начала осуществлять смелый план развития.","en":"The company began to carry out a bold development plan.","de":"Das Unternehmen begann, einen kühnen Entwicklungsplan durchzuführen.","it":"L'azienda ha iniziato a realizzare un audace piano di sviluppo.","es_ar":"La empresa empezó a llevar a cabo un audaz plan de desarrollo.","fr":"L'entreprise a commencé à réaliser un plan de développement audacieux."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"спростовувати","level":"B1","ru":"опровергать","en":"to refute","de":"widerlegen","it":"confutare","es_ar":"refutar","fr":"réfuter","examples":[{"uk":"Учені намагаються спростовувати цю теорію новими фактами.","ru":"Учёные пытаются опровергать эту теорию новыми фактами.","en":"Scientists are trying to refute this theory with new facts.","de":"Wissenschaftler versuchen, diese Theorie mit neuen Fakten zu widerlegen.","it":"Gli scienziati cercano di confutare questa teoria con nuovi fatti.","es_ar":"Los científicos intentan refutar esta teoría con nuevos hechos.","fr":"Les scientifiques essaient de réfuter cette théorie avec de nouveaux faits."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas","language-words"]},
{"word":"зважати","level":"B1","ru":"учитывать","en":"to take into account","de":"berücksichtigen","it":"tenere conto","es_ar":"tener en cuenta","fr":"tenir compte","examples":[{"uk":"Приймаючи рішення, важливо зважати на думку колег.","ru":"Принимая решение, важно учитывать мнение коллег.","en":"When making a decision, it is important to take colleagues' opinions into account.","de":"Bei einer Entscheidung ist es wichtig, die Meinung der Kollegen zu berücksichtigen.","it":"Nel prendere una decisione, è importante tenere conto dell'opinione dei colleghi.","es_ar":"Al tomar una decisión, es importante tener en cuenta la opinión de los colegas.","fr":"En prenant une décision, il est important de tenir compte de l'avis des collègues."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"втручатися","level":"B1","ru":"вмешиваться","en":"to interfere","de":"sich einmischen","it":"intromettersi","es_ar":"entrometerse","fr":"s'immiscer","examples":[{"uk":"Не варто втручатися в чужі сімейні справи.","ru":"Не стоит вмешиваться в чужие семейные дела.","en":"You shouldn't interfere in other people's family affairs.","de":"Man sollte sich nicht in fremde Familienangelegenheiten einmischen.","it":"Non bisogna intromettersi negli affari di famiglia altrui.","es_ar":"No conviene entrometerse en los asuntos familiares ajenos.","fr":"Il ne faut pas s'immiscer dans les affaires familiales des autres."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"вдосконалювати","level":"B1","ru":"совершенствовать","en":"to improve","de":"vervollkommnen","it":"perfezionare","es_ar":"perfeccionar","fr":"perfectionner","examples":[{"uk":"Щоб вільно говорити, потрібно постійно вдосконалювати свою вимову.","ru":"Чтобы свободно говорить, нужно постоянно совершенствовать своё произношение.","en":"To speak fluently, you need to constantly improve your pronunciation.","de":"Um fließend zu sprechen, muss man ständig seine Aussprache vervollkommnen.","it":"Per parlare fluentemente, bisogna perfezionare costantemente la propria pronuncia.","es_ar":"Para hablar con fluidez, hay que perfeccionar constantemente la pronunciación.","fr":"Pour parler couramment, il faut sans cesse perfectionner sa prononciation."}],"syn":["удосконалювати"],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"перешкоджати","level":"B1","ru":"мешать","en":"to hinder","de":"behindern","it":"ostacolare","es_ar":"obstaculizar","fr":"entraver","examples":[{"uk":"Гучний шум за вікном перешкоджав мені зосередитися.","ru":"Громкий шум за окном мешал мне сосредоточиться.","en":"The loud noise outside the window hindered me from concentrating.","de":"Der laute Lärm vor dem Fenster hinderte mich daran, mich zu konzentrieren.","it":"Il forte rumore fuori dalla finestra mi impediva di concentrarmi.","es_ar":"El fuerte ruido fuera de la ventana me impedía concentrarme.","fr":"Le bruit fort à l'extérieur de la fenêtre m'empêchait de me concentrer."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"узгоджувати","level":"B1","ru":"согласовывать","en":"to coordinate","de":"abstimmen","it":"concordare","es_ar":"coordinar","fr":"coordonner","examples":[{"uk":"Перед поїздкою ми маємо узгоджувати всі деталі з керівником.","ru":"Перед поездкой мы должны согласовывать все детали с руководителем.","en":"Before the trip we have to coordinate all the details with the manager.","de":"Vor der Reise müssen wir alle Einzelheiten mit dem Chef abstimmen.","it":"Prima del viaggio dobbiamo concordare tutti i dettagli con il responsabile.","es_ar":"Antes del viaje debemos coordinar todos los detalles con el jefe.","fr":"Avant le voyage, nous devons coordonner tous les détails avec le responsable."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"спонукати","level":"B1","ru":"побуждать","en":"to encourage","de":"veranlassen","it":"spingere","es_ar":"impulsar","fr":"inciter","examples":[{"uk":"Цікава книга може спонукати дитину читати більше.","ru":"Интересная книга может побуждать ребёнка читать больше.","en":"An interesting book can encourage a child to read more.","de":"Ein interessantes Buch kann ein Kind dazu veranlassen, mehr zu lesen.","it":"Un libro interessante può spingere un bambino a leggere di più.","es_ar":"Un libro interesante puede impulsar a un niño a leer más.","fr":"Un livre intéressant peut inciter un enfant à lire davantage."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"зумовлювати","level":"B1","ru":"обусловливать","en":"to determine","de":"bedingen","it":"determinare","es_ar":"condicionar","fr":"conditionner","examples":[{"uk":"Клімат значною мірою зумовлює спосіб життя людей у регіоні.","ru":"Климат в значительной мере обусловливает образ жизни людей в регионе.","en":"The climate largely determines the way of life of people in the region.","de":"Das Klima bedingt weitgehend die Lebensweise der Menschen in der Region.","it":"Il clima determina in gran parte lo stile di vita delle persone nella regione.","es_ar":"El clima condiciona en gran medida el modo de vida de la gente en la región.","fr":"Le climat conditionne en grande partie le mode de vie des gens dans la région."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"засвідчувати","level":"B1","ru":"удостоверять","en":"to certify","de":"bescheinigen","it":"attestare","es_ar":"certificar","fr":"attester","examples":[{"uk":"Нотаріус має засвідчувати справжність вашого підпису.","ru":"Нотариус должен удостоверять подлинность вашей подписи.","en":"A notary must certify the authenticity of your signature.","de":"Ein Notar muss die Echtheit Ihrer Unterschrift bescheinigen.","it":"Un notaio deve attestare l'autenticità della vostra firma.","es_ar":"Un notario debe certificar la autenticidad de su firma.","fr":"Un notaire doit attester l'authenticité de votre signature."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas","law"]},
{"word":"запобігати","level":"B1","ru":"предотвращать","en":"to prevent","de":"verhindern","it":"prevenire","es_ar":"prevenir","fr":"prévenir","examples":[{"uk":"Регулярні огляди допомагають запобігати серйозним хворобам.","ru":"Регулярные осмотры помогают предотвращать серьёзные болезни.","en":"Regular check-ups help to prevent serious illnesses.","de":"Regelmäßige Untersuchungen helfen, schwere Krankheiten zu verhindern.","it":"I controlli regolari aiutano a prevenire malattie gravi.","es_ar":"Los chequeos regulares ayudan a prevenir enfermedades graves.","fr":"Les examens réguliers aident à prévenir les maladies graves."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"пристосовуватися","level":"B1","ru":"приспосабливаться","en":"to adapt","de":"sich anpassen","it":"adattarsi","es_ar":"adaptarse","fr":"s'adapter","examples":[{"uk":"Людині нелегко пристосовуватися до життя в чужій країні.","ru":"Человеку нелегко приспосабливаться к жизни в чужой стране.","en":"It is not easy for a person to adapt to life in a foreign country.","de":"Es ist für einen Menschen nicht leicht, sich an das Leben in einem fremden Land anzupassen.","it":"Non è facile per una persona adattarsi alla vita in un paese straniero.","es_ar":"No es fácil para una persona adaptarse a la vida en un país extranjero.","fr":"Il n'est pas facile pour une personne de s'adapter à la vie dans un pays étranger."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"запевняти","level":"B1","ru":"уверять","en":"to assure","de":"versichern","it":"assicurare","es_ar":"asegurar","fr":"assurer","examples":[{"uk":"Продавець запевняв нас, що товар цілком якісний.","ru":"Продавец уверял нас, что товар вполне качественный.","en":"The salesman assured us that the product was of good quality.","de":"Der Verkäufer versicherte uns, dass die Ware durchaus hochwertig sei.","it":"Il venditore ci assicurava che il prodotto era di buona qualità.","es_ar":"El vendedor nos aseguraba que el producto era de buena calidad.","fr":"Le vendeur nous assurait que le produit était de bonne qualité."}],"topics":["language-words","abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"звинувачувати","level":"B1","ru":"обвинять","en":"to accuse","de":"beschuldigen","it":"accusare","es_ar":"acusar","fr":"accuser","examples":[{"uk":"Не можна звинувачувати людину без доказів.","ru":"Нельзя обвинять человека без доказательств.","en":"You cannot accuse a person without evidence.","de":"Man darf einen Menschen nicht ohne Beweise beschuldigen.","it":"Non si può accusare una persona senza prove.","es_ar":"No se puede acusar a una persona sin pruebas.","fr":"On ne peut pas accuser une personne sans preuves."}],"topics":["language-words","law"]},
{"word":"домагатися","level":"B1","ru":"добиваться","en":"to strive for","de":"erstreben","it":"ottenere","es_ar":"lograr","fr":"s'efforcer d'obtenir","examples":[{"uk":"Наполегливою працею вона домагалася своєї мети.","ru":"Упорным трудом она добивалась своей цели.","en":"Through persistent work she strove to reach her goal.","de":"Durch beharrliche Arbeit erstrebte sie ihr Ziel.","it":"Con un lavoro tenace lei cercava di raggiungere il suo obiettivo.","es_ar":"Con un trabajo tenaz ella se esforzaba por lograr su objetivo.","fr":"Par un travail persévérant, elle s'efforçait d'atteindre son objectif."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"поглиблювати","level":"B1","ru":"углублять","en":"to deepen","de":"vertiefen","it":"approfondire","es_ar":"profundizar","fr":"approfondir","examples":[{"uk":"Курси допомагають студентам поглиблювати знання з мови.","ru":"Курсы помогают студентам углублять знания по языку.","en":"The courses help students to deepen their knowledge of the language.","de":"Die Kurse helfen den Studenten, ihre Sprachkenntnisse zu vertiefen.","it":"I corsi aiutano gli studenti ad approfondire la conoscenza della lingua.","es_ar":"Los cursos ayudan a los estudiantes a profundizar sus conocimientos del idioma.","fr":"Les cours aident les étudiants à approfondir leur connaissance de la langue."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"скорочувати","level":"B1","ru":"сокращать","en":"to reduce","de":"verringern","it":"ridurre","es_ar":"reducir","fr":"réduire","examples":[{"uk":"Фірма вирішила скорочувати витрати на рекламу.","ru":"Фирма решила сокращать расходы на рекламу.","en":"The company decided to reduce its advertising costs.","de":"Die Firma beschloss, die Werbekosten zu verringern.","it":"L'azienda ha deciso di ridurre le spese pubblicitarie.","es_ar":"La empresa decidió reducir los gastos de publicidad.","fr":"L'entreprise a décidé de réduire ses dépenses publicitaires."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"пришвидшувати","level":"B1","ru":"ускорять","en":"to accelerate","de":"beschleunigen","it":"accelerare","es_ar":"acelerar","fr":"accélérer","examples":[{"uk":"Нові технології здатні пришвидшувати роботу всієї команди.","ru":"Новые технологии способны ускорять работу всей команды.","en":"New technologies can accelerate the work of the whole team.","de":"Neue Technologien können die Arbeit des ganzen Teams beschleunigen.","it":"Le nuove tecnologie possono accelerare il lavoro di tutta la squadra.","es_ar":"Las nuevas tecnologías pueden acelerar el trabajo de todo el equipo.","fr":"Les nouvelles technologies peuvent accélérer le travail de toute l'équipe."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"відображати","level":"B1","ru":"отражать","en":"to reflect","de":"widerspiegeln","it":"riflettere","es_ar":"reflejar","fr":"refléter","examples":[{"uk":"Ця стаття добре відображає настрої сучасної молоді.","ru":"Эта статья хорошо отражает настроения современной молодёжи.","en":"This article well reflects the mood of today's youth.","de":"Dieser Artikel spiegelt die Stimmung der heutigen Jugend gut wider.","it":"Questo articolo riflette bene gli umori dei giovani di oggi.","es_ar":"Este artículo refleja bien el estado de ánimo de los jóvenes de hoy.","fr":"Cet article reflète bien l'état d'esprit de la jeunesse d'aujourd'hui."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"зазначати","level":"B1","ru":"отмечать","en":"to note","de":"anmerken","it":"osservare","es_ar":"señalar","fr":"noter","examples":[{"uk":"Автор зазначає, що проблема потребує уваги.","ru":"Автор отмечает, что проблема требует внимания.","en":"The author notes that the problem requires attention.","de":"Der Autor merkt an, dass das Problem Aufmerksamkeit erfordert.","it":"L'autore osserva che il problema richiede attenzione.","es_ar":"El autor señala que el problema requiere atención.","fr":"L'auteur note que le problème nécessite de l'attention."}],"topics":["language-words","abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"свідчити","level":"B1","ru":"свидетельствовать","en":"to testify","de":"bezeugen","it":"testimoniare","es_ar":"atestiguar","fr":"témoigner","examples":[{"uk":"Ці факти свідчать про серйозні зміни в економіці.","ru":"Эти факты свидетельствуют о серьёзных изменениях в экономике.","en":"These facts testify to serious changes in the economy.","de":"Diese Fakten bezeugen ernsthafte Veränderungen in der Wirtschaft.","it":"Questi fatti testimoniano gravi cambiamenti nell'economia.","es_ar":"Estos hechos atestiguan cambios serios en la economía.","fr":"Ces faits témoignent de changements sérieux dans l'économie."}],"topics":["law","language-words"]},
{"word":"забезпечувати","level":"B1","ru":"обеспечивать","en":"to ensure","de":"gewährleisten","it":"garantire","es_ar":"garantizar","fr":"assurer","examples":[{"uk":"Держава повинна забезпечувати безпеку громадян.","ru":"Государство должно обеспечивать безопасность граждан.","en":"The state must ensure the safety of its citizens.","de":"Der Staat muss die Sicherheit der Bürger gewährleisten.","it":"Lo Stato deve garantire la sicurezza dei cittadini.","es_ar":"El Estado debe garantizar la seguridad de los ciudadanos.","fr":"L'État doit assurer la sécurité des citoyens."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"ускладнювати","level":"B1","ru":"усложнять","en":"to complicate","de":"erschweren","it":"complicare","es_ar":"complicar","fr":"compliquer","examples":[{"uk":"Погана погода ускладнює роботу рятувальників.","ru":"Плохая погода усложняет работу спасателей.","en":"Bad weather complicates the work of the rescuers.","de":"Schlechtes Wetter erschwert die Arbeit der Retter.","it":"Il maltempo complica il lavoro dei soccorritori.","es_ar":"El mal tiempo complica el trabajo de los rescatistas.","fr":"Le mauvais temps complique le travail des sauveteurs."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"спрощувати","level":"B1","ru":"упрощать","en":"to simplify","de":"vereinfachen","it":"semplificare","es_ar":"simplificar","fr":"simplifier","examples":[{"uk":"Нова програма спрощує подання документів онлайн.","ru":"Новая программа упрощает подачу документов онлайн.","en":"The new program simplifies submitting documents online.","de":"Das neue Programm vereinfacht das Einreichen von Dokumenten online.","it":"Il nuovo programma semplifica l'invio dei documenti online.","es_ar":"El nuevo programa simplifica la presentación de documentos en línea.","fr":"Le nouveau programme simplifie l'envoi de documents en ligne."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"ризикувати","level":"B1","ru":"рисковать","en":"to risk","de":"riskieren","it":"rischiare","es_ar":"arriesgar","fr":"risquer","examples":[{"uk":"Не варто ризикувати здоров'ям заради грошей.","ru":"Не стоит рисковать здоровьем ради денег.","en":"It is not worth risking your health for money.","de":"Es lohnt sich nicht, seine Gesundheit für Geld zu riskieren.","it":"Non vale la pena rischiare la salute per il denaro.","es_ar":"No vale la pena arriesgar la salud por dinero.","fr":"Cela ne vaut pas la peine de risquer sa santé pour de l'argent."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"здобувати","level":"B1","ru":"приобретать","en":"to gain","de":"erlangen","it":"acquisire","es_ar":"adquirir","fr":"acquérir","examples":[{"uk":"У цьому університеті студенти здобувають цінні знання.","ru":"В этом университете студенты приобретают ценные знания.","en":"At this university, students gain valuable knowledge.","de":"An dieser Universität erlangen die Studenten wertvolles Wissen.","it":"In questa università gli studenti acquisiscono conoscenze preziose.","es_ar":"En esta universidad los estudiantes adquieren conocimientos valiosos.","fr":"Dans cette université, les étudiants acquièrent des connaissances précieuses."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"підкреслювати","level":"B1","ru":"подчёркивать","en":"to emphasize","de":"betonen","it":"sottolineare","es_ar":"subrayar","fr":"souligner","examples":[{"uk":"Учитель завжди підкреслює важливість практики.","ru":"Учитель всегда подчёркивает важность практики.","en":"The teacher always emphasizes the importance of practice.","de":"Der Lehrer betont immer die Bedeutung der Praxis.","it":"L'insegnante sottolinea sempre l'importanza della pratica.","es_ar":"El profesor siempre subraya la importancia de la práctica.","fr":"Le professeur souligne toujours l'importance de la pratique."}],"topics":["language-words","abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"залучати","level":"B1","ru":"привлекать","en":"to involve","de":"einbeziehen","it":"coinvolgere","es_ar":"involucrar","fr":"impliquer","examples":[{"uk":"Організатори прагнуть залучати молодь до волонтерства.","ru":"Организаторы стремятся привлекать молодёжь к волонтёрству.","en":"The organizers strive to involve young people in volunteering.","de":"Die Organisatoren bemühen sich, junge Menschen in die Freiwilligenarbeit einzubeziehen.","it":"Gli organizzatori cercano di coinvolgere i giovani nel volontariato.","es_ar":"Los organizadores buscan involucrar a los jóvenes en el voluntariado.","fr":"Les organisateurs cherchent à impliquer les jeunes dans le bénévolat."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"враховувати","level":"B1","ru":"учитывать","en":"to take into account","de":"berücksichtigen","it":"tenere conto","es_ar":"tener en cuenta","fr":"tenir compte","examples":[{"uk":"Плануючи поїздку, треба враховувати погодні умови.","ru":"Планируя поездку, нужно учитывать погодные условия.","en":"When planning a trip, you must take weather conditions into account.","de":"Bei der Planung einer Reise muss man die Wetterbedingungen berücksichtigen.","it":"Nel pianificare un viaggio bisogna tenere conto delle condizioni meteorologiche.","es_ar":"Al planear un viaje hay que tener en cuenta las condiciones meteorológicas.","fr":"En planifiant un voyage, il faut tenir compte des conditions météorologiques."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"стверджувати","level":"B1","ru":"утверждать","en":"to claim","de":"behaupten","it":"affermare","es_ar":"afirmar","fr":"affirmer","examples":[{"uk":"Учені стверджують, що клімат поступово змінюється.","ru":"Учёные утверждают, что климат постепенно меняется.","en":"Scientists claim that the climate is gradually changing.","de":"Wissenschaftler behaupten, dass sich das Klima allmählich verändert.","it":"Gli scienziati affermano che il clima sta cambiando gradualmente.","es_ar":"Los científicos afirman que el clima está cambiando poco a poco.","fr":"Les scientifiques affirment que le climat change progressivement."}],"topics":["language-words","abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"визначати","level":"B1","ru":"определять","en":"to determine","de":"bestimmen","it":"determinare","es_ar":"determinar","fr":"déterminer","examples":[{"uk":"Результати тесту допомагають визначати рівень знань.","ru":"Результаты теста помогают определять уровень знаний.","en":"The test results help to determine the level of knowledge.","de":"Die Testergebnisse helfen, das Wissensniveau zu bestimmen.","it":"I risultati del test aiutano a determinare il livello di conoscenza.","es_ar":"Los resultados del examen ayudan a determinar el nivel de conocimientos.","fr":"Les résultats du test aident à déterminer le niveau de connaissances."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"переконуватися","level":"B1","ru":"убеждаться","en":"to make sure","de":"sich vergewissern","it":"accertarsi","es_ar":"asegurarse","fr":"s'assurer","examples":[{"uk":"Перед виходом варто переконуватися, що двері зачинені.","ru":"Перед выходом стоит убеждаться, что дверь закрыта.","en":"Before leaving, you should make sure the door is locked.","de":"Vor dem Verlassen sollte man sich vergewissern, dass die Tür geschlossen ist.","it":"Prima di uscire bisogna accertarsi che la porta sia chiusa.","es_ar":"Antes de salir hay que asegurarse de que la puerta esté cerrada.","fr":"Avant de partir, il faut s'assurer que la porte est fermée."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"переживати","level":"B1","ru":"переживать","en":"to worry","de":"sich sorgen","it":"preoccuparsi","es_ar":"preocuparse","fr":"s'inquiéter","examples":[{"uk":"Мама завжди переживає, коли діти повертаються пізно.","ru":"Мама всегда переживает, когда дети возвращаются поздно.","en":"Mom always worries when the children come back late.","de":"Mama sorgt sich immer, wenn die Kinder spät zurückkommen.","it":"La mamma si preoccupa sempre quando i figli tornano tardi.","es_ar":"Mamá siempre se preocupa cuando los niños vuelven tarde.","fr":"Maman s'inquiète toujours quand les enfants rentrent tard."}],"topics":["emotions"]},
{"word":"звертати","level":"B1","ru":"обращать","en":"to pay (attention)","de":"richten","it":"prestare","es_ar":"prestar","fr":"prêter","examples":[{"uk":"Важливо звертати увагу на деталі під час роботи.","ru":"Важно обращать внимание на детали во время работы.","en":"It is important to pay attention to details while working.","de":"Es ist wichtig, bei der Arbeit auf die Details zu achten.","it":"È importante prestare attenzione ai dettagli durante il lavoro.","es_ar":"Es importante prestar atención a los detalles durante el trabajo.","fr":"Il est important de prêter attention aux détails pendant le travail."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"обмежувати","level":"B1","ru":"ограничивать","en":"to limit","de":"einschränken","it":"limitare","es_ar":"limitar","fr":"limiter","examples":[{"uk":"Лікар порадив обмежувати вживання солодкого.","ru":"Врач посоветовал ограничивать употребление сладкого.","en":"The doctor advised to limit the consumption of sweets.","de":"Der Arzt riet, den Verzehr von Süßigkeiten einzuschränken.","it":"Il medico ha consigliato di limitare il consumo di dolci.","es_ar":"El médico aconsejó limitar el consumo de dulces.","fr":"Le médecin a conseillé de limiter la consommation de sucreries."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"долати","level":"B1","ru":"преодолевать","en":"to overcome","de":"überwinden","it":"superare","es_ar":"superar","fr":"surmonter","examples":[{"uk":"Спортсмени вчаться долати труднощі й не здаватися.","ru":"Спортсмены учатся преодолевать трудности и не сдаваться.","en":"Athletes learn to overcome difficulties and not give up.","de":"Sportler lernen, Schwierigkeiten zu überwinden und nicht aufzugeben.","it":"Gli atleti imparano a superare le difficoltà e a non arrendersi.","es_ar":"Los deportistas aprenden a superar las dificultades y a no rendirse.","fr":"Les sportifs apprennent à surmonter les difficultés et à ne pas abandonner."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"поводитися","level":"B1","ru":"вести себя","en":"to behave","de":"sich verhalten","it":"comportarsi","es_ar":"comportarse","fr":"se comporter","examples":[{"uk":"Діти вміють гарно поводитися в громадських місцях.","ru":"Дети умеют хорошо вести себя в общественных местах.","en":"The children know how to behave well in public places.","de":"Die Kinder wissen, wie man sich an öffentlichen Orten gut verhält.","it":"I bambini sanno comportarsi bene nei luoghi pubblici.","es_ar":"Los niños saben comportarse bien en lugares públicos.","fr":"Les enfants savent bien se comporter dans les lieux publics."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas","emotions"]},
{"word":"сприяти","level":"B1","ru":"способствовать","en":"to contribute","de":"beitragen","it":"contribuire","es_ar":"contribuir","fr":"contribuer","examples":[{"uk":"Регулярні прогулянки сприяють міцному здоров'ю.","ru":"Регулярные прогулки способствуют крепкому здоровью.","en":"Regular walks contribute to good health.","de":"Regelmäßige Spaziergänge tragen zu einer guten Gesundheit bei.","it":"Le passeggiate regolari contribuiscono a una buona salute.","es_ar":"Los paseos regulares contribuyen a una buena salud.","fr":"Les promenades régulières contribuent à une bonne santé."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"втілювати","level":"B1","ru":"воплощать","en":"to embody","de":"verkörpern","it":"incarnare","es_ar":"encarnar","fr":"incarner","examples":[{"uk":"Цей герой втілює ідеали свого часу.","ru":"Этот герой воплощает идеалы своего времени.","en":"This hero embodies the ideals of his time.","de":"Dieser Held verkörpert die Ideale seiner Zeit.","it":"Questo eroe incarna gli ideali del suo tempo.","es_ar":"Este héroe encarna los ideales de su época.","fr":"Ce héros incarne les idéaux de son époque."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"запозичувати","level":"B1","ru":"заимствовать","en":"to borrow (adopt)","de":"entlehnen","it":"prendere in prestito","es_ar":"tomar prestado","fr":"emprunter","examples":[{"uk":"Багато слів українська мова запозичила з латини.","ru":"Многие слова украинский язык заимствовал из латыни.","en":"The Ukrainian language borrowed many words from Latin.","de":"Die ukrainische Sprache hat viele Wörter aus dem Lateinischen entlehnt.","it":"La lingua ucraina ha preso in prestito molte parole dal latino.","es_ar":"El idioma ucraniano tomó prestadas muchas palabras del latín.","fr":"La langue ukrainienne a emprunté beaucoup de mots au latin."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas","language-words"]},
{"word":"успадковувати","level":"B1","ru":"наследовать","en":"to inherit","de":"erben","it":"ereditare","es_ar":"heredar","fr":"hériter","examples":[{"uk":"Діти часто успадковують риси характеру батьків.","ru":"Дети часто наследуют черты характера родителей.","en":"Children often inherit their parents' character traits.","de":"Kinder erben oft die Charakterzüge ihrer Eltern.","it":"I bambini spesso ereditano i tratti caratteriali dei genitori.","es_ar":"Los niños a menudo heredan los rasgos de carácter de sus padres.","fr":"Les enfants héritent souvent des traits de caractère de leurs parents."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas","biology"]},
{"word":"вшановувати","level":"B1","ru":"чтить","en":"to honor","de":"ehren","it":"onorare","es_ar":"honrar","fr":"honorer","examples":[{"uk":"Щороку люди вшановують пам'ять загиблих героїв.","ru":"Каждый год люди чтят память погибших героев.","en":"Every year people honor the memory of the fallen heroes.","de":"Jedes Jahr ehren die Menschen das Andenken an die gefallenen Helden.","it":"Ogni anno le persone onorano la memoria degli eroi caduti.","es_ar":"Cada año la gente honra la memoria de los héroes caídos.","fr":"Chaque année, les gens honorent la mémoire des héros tombés."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas","relationships"]},
{"word":"занепадати","level":"B1","ru":"приходить в упадок","en":"to decline (decay)","de":"verfallen","it":"decadere","es_ar":"decaer","fr":"décliner","examples":[{"uk":"Без інвестицій місто поступово занепадало.","ru":"Без инвестиций город постепенно приходил в упадок.","en":"Without investment, the town gradually declined.","de":"Ohne Investitionen verfiel die Stadt allmählich.","it":"Senza investimenti, la città decadeva gradualmente.","es_ar":"Sin inversiones, la ciudad decaía gradualmente.","fr":"Sans investissements, la ville déclinait peu à peu."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"зволікати","level":"B1","ru":"медлить","en":"to procrastinate","de":"zögern","it":"indugiare","es_ar":"demorar","fr":"tarder","examples":[{"uk":"Не варто зволікати з ухваленням рішення.","ru":"Не стоит медлить с принятием решения.","en":"You shouldn't procrastinate in making a decision.","de":"Man sollte mit der Entscheidung nicht zögern.","it":"Non conviene indugiare nel prendere una decisione.","es_ar":"No conviene demorar la toma de una decisión.","fr":"Il ne faut pas tarder à prendre une décision."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"вирізнятися","level":"B1","ru":"выделяться","en":"to stand out","de":"sich abheben","it":"distinguersi","es_ar":"destacarse","fr":"se distinguer","examples":[{"uk":"Її робота вирізняється серед інших оригінальністю.","ru":"Её работа выделяется среди других оригинальностью.","en":"Her work stands out from the others by its originality.","de":"Ihre Arbeit hebt sich durch ihre Originalität von den anderen ab.","it":"Il suo lavoro si distingue dagli altri per l'originalità.","es_ar":"Su trabajo se destaca entre los demás por su originalidad.","fr":"Son travail se distingue des autres par son originalité."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"згуртовувати","level":"B1","ru":"сплачивать","en":"to unite (rally)","de":"zusammenschweißen","it":"unire","es_ar":"unir","fr":"rassembler","examples":[{"uk":"Спільна мета згуртовує колектив.","ru":"Общая цель сплачивает коллектив.","en":"A common goal unites the team.","de":"Ein gemeinsames Ziel schweißt das Team zusammen.","it":"Un obiettivo comune unisce la squadra.","es_ar":"Un objetivo común une al equipo.","fr":"Un objectif commun rassemble l'équipe."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas","relationships"]},
{"word":"нехтувати","level":"B1","ru":"пренебрегать","en":"to neglect","de":"vernachlässigen","it":"trascurare","es_ar":"descuidar","fr":"négliger","examples":[{"uk":"Не можна нехтувати правилами безпеки.","ru":"Нельзя пренебрегать правилами безопасности.","en":"You must not neglect the safety rules.","de":"Man darf die Sicherheitsregeln nicht vernachlässigen.","it":"Non si devono trascurare le norme di sicurezza.","es_ar":"No se deben descuidar las reglas de seguridad.","fr":"Il ne faut pas négliger les règles de sécurité."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"виснажувати","level":"B1","ru":"истощать","en":"to exhaust (deplete)","de":"erschöpfen","it":"esaurire","es_ar":"agotar","fr":"épuiser","examples":[{"uk":"Надмірне видобування виснажує природні ресурси.","ru":"Чрезмерная добыча истощает природные ресурсы.","en":"Excessive extraction depletes natural resources.","de":"Übermäßiger Abbau erschöpft die natürlichen Ressourcen.","it":"L'estrazione eccessiva esaurisce le risorse naturali.","es_ar":"La extracción excesiva agota los recursos naturales.","fr":"L'extraction excessive épuise les ressources naturelles."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"розчаровувати","level":"B1","ru":"разочаровывать","en":"to disappoint","de":"enttäuschen","it":"deludere","es_ar":"decepcionar","fr":"décevoir","examples":[{"uk":"Фінал фільму розчарував багатьох глядачів.","ru":"Финал фильма разочаровал многих зрителей.","en":"The ending of the film disappointed many viewers.","de":"Das Ende des Films enttäuschte viele Zuschauer.","it":"Il finale del film ha deluso molti spettatori.","es_ar":"El final de la película decepcionó a muchos espectadores.","fr":"La fin du film a déçu de nombreux spectateurs."}],"topics":["emotions"]},
{"word":"позбавляти","level":"B1","ru":"лишать","en":"to deprive","de":"berauben","it":"privare","es_ar":"privar","fr":"priver","examples":[{"uk":"Суд може позбавити водія прав на рік.","ru":"Суд может лишить водителя прав на год.","en":"The court may deprive the driver of their license for a year.","de":"Das Gericht kann dem Fahrer den Führerschein für ein Jahr entziehen.","it":"Il tribunale può privare l'automobilista della patente per un anno.","es_ar":"El tribunal puede privar al conductor de su licencia por un año.","fr":"Le tribunal peut priver le conducteur de son permis pendant un an."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"позбуватися","level":"B1","ru":"избавляться","en":"to get rid of","de":"loswerden","it":"liberarsi","es_ar":"deshacerse","fr":"se débarrasser","examples":[{"uk":"Важко позбуватися шкідливих звичок.","ru":"Трудно избавляться от вредных привычек.","en":"It is hard to get rid of bad habits.","de":"Es ist schwer, schlechte Gewohnheiten loszuwerden.","it":"È difficile liberarsi delle cattive abitudini.","es_ar":"Es difícil deshacerse de los malos hábitos.","fr":"Il est difficile de se débarrasser des mauvaises habitudes."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"загострювати","level":"B1","ru":"обострять","en":"to aggravate","de":"verschärfen","it":"aggravare","es_ar":"agravar","fr":"aggraver","examples":[{"uk":"Нові санкції загострили економічну кризу.","ru":"Новые санкции обострили экономический кризис.","en":"The new sanctions aggravated the economic crisis.","de":"Die neuen Sanktionen verschärften die Wirtschaftskrise.","it":"Le nuove sanzioni hanno aggravato la crisi economica.","es_ar":"Las nuevas sanciones agravaron la crisis económica.","fr":"Les nouvelles sanctions ont aggravé la crise économique."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"пом'якшувати","level":"B1","ru":"смягчать","en":"to soften (mitigate)","de":"mildern","it":"attenuare","es_ar":"suavizar","fr":"atténuer","examples":[{"uk":"Ліси пом'якшують клімат у регіоні.","ru":"Леса смягчают климат в регионе.","en":"Forests soften the climate in the region.","de":"Wälder mildern das Klima in der Region.","it":"Le foreste attenuano il clima nella regione.","es_ar":"Los bosques suavizan el clima en la región.","fr":"Les forêts atténuent le climat de la région."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"окреслювати","level":"B1","ru":"очерчивать","en":"to outline","de":"umreißen","it":"delineare","es_ar":"esbozar","fr":"esquisser","examples":[{"uk":"У вступі автор окреслює головні завдання дослідження.","ru":"Во введении автор очерчивает главные задачи исследования.","en":"In the introduction, the author outlines the main goals of the study.","de":"In der Einleitung umreißt der Autor die Hauptziele der Studie.","it":"Nell'introduzione l'autore delinea gli obiettivi principali della ricerca.","es_ar":"En la introducción, el autor esboza los principales objetivos del estudio.","fr":"Dans l'introduction, l'auteur esquisse les principaux objectifs de l'étude."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas","language-words"]},
{"word":"знецінювати","level":"B1","ru":"обесценивать","en":"to devalue","de":"entwerten","it":"svalutare","es_ar":"devaluar","fr":"dévaloriser","examples":[{"uk":"Інфляція швидко знецінює заощадження людей.","ru":"Инфляция быстро обесценивает сбережения людей.","en":"Inflation quickly devalues people's savings.","de":"Die Inflation entwertet rasch die Ersparnisse der Menschen.","it":"L'inflazione svaluta rapidamente i risparmi della gente.","es_ar":"La inflación devalúa rápidamente los ahorros de la gente.","fr":"L'inflation dévalorise rapidement les économies des gens."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas","economy-finance"]},
{"word":"умовляти","level":"B1","ru":"уговаривать","en":"to talk into (persuade)","de":"überreden","it":"convincere","es_ar":"persuadir","fr":"persuader","examples":[{"uk":"Друзі довго умовляли мене поїхати з ними.","ru":"Друзья долго уговаривали меня поехать с ними.","en":"My friends spent a long time talking me into going with them.","de":"Meine Freunde haben mich lange überredet, mit ihnen zu fahren.","it":"Gli amici mi hanno convinto a lungo ad andare con loro.","es_ar":"Mis amigos me persuadieron durante mucho tiempo de ir con ellos.","fr":"Mes amis ont longtemps cherché à me persuader de partir avec eux."}],"topics":["language-words"]},
{"word":"вгамовувати","level":"B1","ru":"унимать","en":"to calm (quell)","de":"beruhigen","it":"placare","es_ar":"calmar","fr":"apaiser","examples":[{"uk":"Мати намагалася вгамувати переляканих дітей.","ru":"Мать пыталась унять испуганных детей.","en":"The mother tried to calm the frightened children.","de":"Die Mutter versuchte, die verängstigten Kinder zu beruhigen.","it":"La madre cercava di placare i bambini spaventati.","es_ar":"La madre intentaba calmar a los niños asustados.","fr":"La mère essayait d'apaiser les enfants effrayés."}],"topics":["emotions"]},
{"word":"споживати","level":"B1","ru":"потреблять","en":"to consume","de":"konsumieren","it":"consumare","es_ar":"consumir","fr":"consommer","examples":[{"uk":"Сучасні прилади споживають менше електроенергії.","ru":"Современные приборы потребляют меньше электроэнергии.","en":"Modern appliances consume less electricity.","de":"Moderne Geräte konsumieren weniger Strom.","it":"Gli apparecchi moderni consumano meno energia elettrica.","es_ar":"Los aparatos modernos consumen menos electricidad.","fr":"Les appareils modernes consomment moins d'électricité."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas","economy-finance"]},
{"word":"набувати","level":"B1","ru":"приобретать","en":"to acquire","de":"erwerben","it":"acquisire","es_ar":"adquirir","fr":"acquérir","examples":[{"uk":"З роками він набув цінного досвіду.","ru":"С годами он приобрёл ценный опыт.","en":"Over the years he acquired valuable experience.","de":"Im Laufe der Jahre erwarb er wertvolle Erfahrung.","it":"Con gli anni ha acquisito un'esperienza preziosa.","es_ar":"Con los años adquirió una experiencia valiosa.","fr":"Au fil des années, il a acquis une expérience précieuse."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"вкорінюватися","level":"B1","ru":"укореняться","en":"to take root","de":"Wurzeln schlagen","it":"radicarsi","es_ar":"arraigarse","fr":"s'enraciner","examples":[{"uk":"Демократичні цінності повільно вкорінюються в суспільстві.","ru":"Демократические ценности медленно укореняются в обществе.","en":"Democratic values slowly take root in society.","de":"Demokratische Werte schlagen langsam Wurzeln in der Gesellschaft.","it":"I valori democratici si radicano lentamente nella società.","es_ar":"Los valores democráticos se arraigan lentamente en la sociedad.","fr":"Les valeurs démocratiques s'enracinent lentement dans la société."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"загартовувати","level":"B1","ru":"закалять","en":"to temper (harden)","de":"abhärten","it":"temprare","es_ar":"templar","fr":"endurcir","examples":[{"uk":"Труднощі загартовують характер людини.","ru":"Трудности закаляют характер человека.","en":"Hardships temper a person's character.","de":"Schwierigkeiten härten den Charakter eines Menschen ab.","it":"Le difficoltà temprano il carattere di una persona.","es_ar":"Las dificultades templan el carácter de una persona.","fr":"Les épreuves endurcissent le caractère d'une personne."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas","body-health"]},
{"word":"відлякувати","level":"B1","ru":"отпугивать","en":"to deter (scare off)","de":"abschrecken","it":"scoraggiare","es_ar":"ahuyentar","fr":"dissuader","examples":[{"uk":"Високі ціни відлякують потенційних покупців.","ru":"Высокие цены отпугивают потенциальных покупателей.","en":"High prices deter potential buyers.","de":"Hohe Preise schrecken potenzielle Käufer ab.","it":"I prezzi elevati scoraggiano i potenziali acquirenti.","es_ar":"Los precios altos ahuyentan a los posibles compradores.","fr":"Les prix élevés dissuadent les acheteurs potentiels."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"посягати","level":"B1","ru":"посягать","en":"to encroach (on)","de":"sich vergreifen an","it":"attentare","es_ar":"atentar","fr":"porter atteinte","examples":[{"uk":"Ніхто не має права посягати на чужу свободу.","ru":"Никто не имеет права посягать на чужую свободу.","en":"No one has the right to encroach on another's freedom.","de":"Niemand hat das Recht, sich an der Freiheit eines anderen zu vergreifen.","it":"Nessuno ha il diritto di attentare alla libertà altrui.","es_ar":"Nadie tiene derecho a atentar contra la libertad ajena.","fr":"Personne n'a le droit de porter atteinte à la liberté d'autrui."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas","law"]},
{"word":"розгортати","level":"B1","ru":"разворачивать","en":"to unfold (deploy)","de":"entfalten","it":"dispiegare","es_ar":"desplegar","fr":"déployer","examples":[{"uk":"Компанія розгортає нову мережу магазинів по всій країні.","ru":"Компания разворачивает новую сеть магазинов по всей стране.","en":"The company is deploying a new network of stores across the country.","de":"Das Unternehmen entfaltet ein neues Filialnetz im ganzen Land.","it":"L'azienda sta dispiegando una nuova rete di negozi in tutto il paese.","es_ar":"La empresa está desplegando una nueva red de tiendas por todo el país.","fr":"L'entreprise déploie un nouveau réseau de magasins dans tout le pays."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"насичувати","level":"B1","ru":"насыщать","en":"to saturate","de":"sättigen","it":"saturare","es_ar":"saturar","fr":"saturer","examples":[{"uk":"Рослини насичують повітря киснем.","ru":"Растения насыщают воздух кислородом.","en":"Plants saturate the air with oxygen.","de":"Pflanzen sättigen die Luft mit Sauerstoff.","it":"Le piante saturano l'aria di ossigeno.","es_ar":"Las plantas saturan el aire de oxígeno.","fr":"Les plantes saturent l'air d'oxygène."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"згасати","level":"B1","ru":"угасать","en":"to fade (die down)","de":"erlöschen","it":"spegnersi","es_ar":"apagarse","fr":"s'éteindre","examples":[{"uk":"Надвечір вогнище поволі згасало.","ru":"К вечеру костёр медленно угасал.","en":"Toward evening the campfire slowly faded.","de":"Gegen Abend erlosch das Lagerfeuer langsam.","it":"Verso sera il falò si spegneva lentamente.","es_ar":"Hacia la tarde la fogata se apagaba lentamente.","fr":"Vers le soir, le feu de camp s'éteignait lentement."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"вирувати","level":"B1","ru":"бурлить","en":"to seethe (rage)","de":"toben","it":"ribollire","es_ar":"bullir","fr":"bouillonner","examples":[{"uk":"На площі вирувало багатотисячне життя.","ru":"На площади бурлила многотысячная жизнь.","en":"Life of many thousands seethed on the square.","de":"Auf dem Platz tobte das Leben von Tausenden.","it":"Sulla piazza ribolliva la vita di migliaia di persone.","es_ar":"En la plaza bullía la vida de miles de personas.","fr":"Sur la place bouillonnait la vie de milliers de gens."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"струшувати","level":"B1","ru":"стряхивать","en":"to shake off","de":"abschütteln","it":"scuotere via","es_ar":"sacudir","fr":"secouer","examples":[{"uk":"Він струсив сніг з плечей і зайшов до хати.","ru":"Он стряхнул снег с плеч и вошёл в дом.","en":"He shook the snow off his shoulders and entered the house.","de":"Er schüttelte den Schnee von den Schultern und trat ins Haus.","it":"Scosse via la neve dalle spalle ed entrò in casa.","es_ar":"Se sacudió la nieve de los hombros y entró en la casa.","fr":"Il secoua la neige de ses épaules et entra dans la maison."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"відмежовувати","level":"B1","ru":"отграничивать","en":"to demarcate (dissociate)","de":"abgrenzen","it":"delimitare","es_ar":"delimitar","fr":"délimiter","examples":[{"uk":"Автор чітко відмежовує факти від власних припущень.","ru":"Автор чётко отграничивает факты от собственных предположений.","en":"The author clearly demarcates facts from their own assumptions.","de":"Der Autor grenzt Fakten klar von eigenen Annahmen ab.","it":"L'autore delimita chiaramente i fatti dalle proprie supposizioni.","es_ar":"El autor delimita claramente los hechos de sus propias suposiciones.","fr":"L'auteur délimite clairement les faits de ses propres suppositions."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"розмежовувати","level":"B1","ru":"разграничивать","en":"to delineate (separate)","de":"trennen","it":"distinguere","es_ar":"separar","fr":"séparer","examples":[{"uk":"Важливо розмежовувати особисте життя і роботу.","ru":"Важно разграничивать личную жизнь и работу.","en":"It is important to delineate personal life and work.","de":"Es ist wichtig, Privatleben und Arbeit zu trennen.","it":"È importante distinguere la vita privata dal lavoro.","es_ar":"Es importante separar la vida personal del trabajo.","fr":"Il est important de séparer la vie privée et le travail."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"заручатися","level":"B1","ru":"заручаться","en":"to enlist (secure support)","de":"sich sichern","it":"assicurarsi","es_ar":"asegurarse","fr":"s'assurer","examples":[{"uk":"Перед виступом він заручився підтримкою колег.","ru":"Перед выступлением он заручился поддержкой коллег.","en":"Before the speech he enlisted the support of his colleagues.","de":"Vor der Rede sicherte er sich die Unterstützung seiner Kollegen.","it":"Prima del discorso si assicurò il sostegno dei colleghi.","es_ar":"Antes del discurso se aseguró el apoyo de sus colegas.","fr":"Avant le discours, il s'est assuré le soutien de ses collègues."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"підважувати","level":"B1","ru":"подрывать","en":"to undermine","de":"untergraben","it":"minare","es_ar":"socavar","fr":"saper","examples":[{"uk":"Такі чутки підважують довіру до влади.","ru":"Такие слухи подрывают доверие к власти.","en":"Such rumors undermine trust in the government.","de":"Solche Gerüchte untergraben das Vertrauen in die Regierung.","it":"Tali voci minano la fiducia nel governo.","es_ar":"Tales rumores socavan la confianza en el gobierno.","fr":"De telles rumeurs sapent la confiance dans le gouvernement."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"затьмарювати","level":"B1","ru":"затмевать","en":"to overshadow","de":"überschatten","it":"offuscare","es_ar":"eclipsar","fr":"éclipser","examples":[{"uk":"Успіх сина затьмарив усі попередні досягнення родини.","ru":"Успех сына затмил все прежние достижения семьи.","en":"The son's success overshadowed all the family's previous achievements.","de":"Der Erfolg des Sohnes überschattete alle früheren Erfolge der Familie.","it":"Il successo del figlio offuscò tutti i precedenti traguardi della famiglia.","es_ar":"El éxito del hijo eclipsó todos los logros anteriores de la familia.","fr":"Le succès du fils a éclipsé tous les exploits précédents de la famille."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"споряджати","level":"B1","ru":"снаряжать","en":"to equip","de":"ausrüsten","it":"equipaggiare","es_ar":"equipar","fr":"équiper","examples":[{"uk":"Волонтери споряджали експедицію в гори.","ru":"Волонтёры снаряжали экспедицию в горы.","en":"The volunteers equipped the expedition to the mountains.","de":"Die Freiwilligen rüsteten die Expedition ins Gebirge aus.","it":"I volontari equipaggiavano la spedizione in montagna.","es_ar":"Los voluntarios equipaban la expedición a las montañas.","fr":"Les bénévoles équipaient l'expédition en montagne."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas","tools-materials"]},
{"word":"втамовувати","level":"B1","ru":"утолять","en":"to quench (satisfy)","de":"stillen","it":"saziare","es_ar":"saciar","fr":"étancher","examples":[{"uk":"Холодна вода добре втамовує спрагу в спеку.","ru":"Холодная вода хорошо утоляет жажду в жару.","en":"Cold water quenches thirst well in the heat.","de":"Kaltes Wasser stillt bei Hitze gut den Durst.","it":"L'acqua fredda sazia bene la sete con il caldo.","es_ar":"El agua fría sacia bien la sed con el calor.","fr":"L'eau froide étanche bien la soif par temps de chaleur."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"згладжувати","level":"B1","ru":"сглаживать","en":"to smooth over","de":"glätten","it":"appianare","es_ar":"limar","fr":"aplanir","examples":[{"uk":"Дипломат намагався згладити гострі суперечності.","ru":"Дипломат пытался сгладить острые противоречия.","en":"The diplomat tried to smooth over the sharp disagreements.","de":"Der Diplomat versuchte, die scharfen Widersprüche zu glätten.","it":"Il diplomatico cercava di appianare i forti contrasti.","es_ar":"El diplomático intentaba limar las agudas discrepancias.","fr":"Le diplomate essayait d'aplanir les vives divergences."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"знеславлювати","level":"B1","ru":"порочить","en":"to defame","de":"verleumden","it":"diffamare","es_ar":"difamar","fr":"diffamer","examples":[{"uk":"Він подав до суду на тих, хто знеславлював його ім'я.","ru":"Он подал в суд на тех, кто порочил его имя.","en":"He sued those who defamed his name.","de":"Er verklagte diejenigen, die seinen Namen verleumdeten.","it":"Fece causa a coloro che diffamavano il suo nome.","es_ar":"Demandó a quienes difamaban su nombre.","fr":"Il a poursuivi ceux qui diffamaient son nom."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas","language-words"]},
{"word":"уподібнювати","level":"B1","ru":"уподоблять","en":"to liken (assimilate)","de":"gleichsetzen","it":"assimilare","es_ar":"asemejar","fr":"assimiler","examples":[{"uk":"Поет уподібнює життя людини до річки.","ru":"Поэт уподобляет жизнь человека реке.","en":"The poet likens human life to a river.","de":"Der Dichter setzt das menschliche Leben einem Fluss gleich.","it":"Il poeta assimila la vita umana a un fiume.","es_ar":"El poeta asemeja la vida humana a un río.","fr":"Le poète assimile la vie humaine à un fleuve."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"узагальнювати","level":"B1","ru":"обобщать","en":"to generalize","de":"verallgemeinern","it":"generalizzare","es_ar":"generalizar","fr":"généraliser","examples":[{"uk":"Не варто узагальнювати на основі одного випадку.","ru":"Не стоит обобщать на основе одного случая.","en":"You shouldn't generalize based on a single case.","de":"Man sollte nicht aufgrund eines einzigen Falls verallgemeinern.","it":"Non bisogna generalizzare sulla base di un solo caso.","es_ar":"No conviene generalizar a partir de un solo caso.","fr":"Il ne faut pas généraliser à partir d'un seul cas."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"деталізувати","level":"B1","ru":"детализировать","en":"to detail","de":"detaillieren","it":"dettagliare","es_ar":"detallar","fr":"détailler","examples":[{"uk":"Прошу деталізувати ваш план дій.","ru":"Прошу детализировать ваш план действий.","en":"Please detail your action plan.","de":"Bitte detaillieren Sie Ihren Aktionsplan.","it":"La prego di dettagliare il suo piano d'azione.","es_ar":"Por favor, detalle su plan de acción.","fr":"Veuillez détailler votre plan d'action."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"класифікувати","level":"B1","ru":"классифицировать","en":"to classify","de":"klassifizieren","it":"classificare","es_ar":"clasificar","fr":"classer","examples":[{"uk":"Науковці класифікують рослини за родинами.","ru":"Учёные классифицируют растения по семействам.","en":"Scientists classify plants by families.","de":"Wissenschaftler klassifizieren Pflanzen nach Familien.","it":"Gli scienziati classificano le piante per famiglie.","es_ar":"Los científicos clasifican las plantas por familias.","fr":"Les scientifiques classent les plantes par familles."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas","science"]},
{"word":"поєднувати","level":"B1","ru":"сочетать","en":"to combine","de":"verbinden","it":"combinare","es_ar":"combinar","fr":"combiner","examples":[{"uk":"Вона вміє поєднувати роботу й навчання.","ru":"Она умеет сочетать работу и учёбу.","en":"She knows how to combine work and studies.","de":"Sie versteht es, Arbeit und Studium zu verbinden.","it":"Lei sa combinare lavoro e studio.","es_ar":"Ella sabe combinar el trabajo y los estudios.","fr":"Elle sait combiner le travail et les études."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"зіставляти","level":"B1","ru":"сопоставлять","en":"to compare","de":"gegenüberstellen","it":"confrontare","es_ar":"cotejar","fr":"comparer","examples":[{"uk":"Аналітик зіставляє дані за кілька років.","ru":"Аналитик сопоставляет данные за несколько лет.","en":"The analyst compares data from several years.","de":"Der Analyst stellt die Daten mehrerer Jahre gegenüber.","it":"L'analista confronta i dati di diversi anni.","es_ar":"El analista coteja los datos de varios años.","fr":"L'analyste compare les données de plusieurs années."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"протиставляти","level":"B1","ru":"противопоставлять","en":"to contrast","de":"entgegensetzen","it":"contrapporre","es_ar":"contraponer","fr":"opposer","examples":[{"uk":"Автор протиставляє місто селу.","ru":"Автор противопоставляет город деревне.","en":"The author contrasts the city with the countryside.","de":"Der Autor stellt die Stadt dem Land gegenüber.","it":"L'autore contrappone la città alla campagna.","es_ar":"El autor contrapone la ciudad al campo.","fr":"L'auteur oppose la ville à la campagne."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"впорядковувати","level":"B1","ru":"упорядочивать","en":"to arrange","de":"ordnen","it":"ordinare","es_ar":"ordenar","fr":"ordonner","examples":[{"uk":"Секретар впорядковує документи за датами.","ru":"Секретарь упорядочивает документы по датам.","en":"The secretary arranges the documents by date.","de":"Der Sekretär ordnet die Dokumente nach Datum.","it":"Il segretario ordina i documenti per data.","es_ar":"El secretario ordena los documentos por fecha.","fr":"Le secrétaire classe les documents par date."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"систематизувати","level":"B1","ru":"систематизировать","en":"to systematize","de":"systematisieren","it":"sistematizzare","es_ar":"sistematizar","fr":"systématiser","examples":[{"uk":"Треба систематизувати зібраний матеріал.","ru":"Нужно систематизировать собранный материал.","en":"We need to systematize the collected material.","de":"Man muss das gesammelte Material systematisieren.","it":"Bisogna sistematizzare il materiale raccolto.","es_ar":"Hay que sistematizar el material recopilado.","fr":"Il faut systématiser le matériel recueilli."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas","science"]},
{"word":"прогнозувати","level":"B1","ru":"прогнозировать","en":"to forecast","de":"prognostizieren","it":"prevedere","es_ar":"pronosticar","fr":"prévoir","examples":[{"uk":"Синоптики прогнозують потепління.","ru":"Синоптики прогнозируют потепление.","en":"Meteorologists forecast a warming.","de":"Die Meteorologen prognostizieren eine Erwärmung.","it":"I meteorologi prevedono un riscaldamento.","es_ar":"Los meteorólogos pronostican un aumento de la temperatura.","fr":"Les météorologues prévoient un réchauffement."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"розраховувати","level":"B1","ru":"рассчитывать","en":"to count on","de":"rechnen mit","it":"contare su","es_ar":"contar con","fr":"compter sur","examples":[{"uk":"Ми розраховуємо на вашу підтримку.","ru":"Мы рассчитываем на вашу поддержку.","en":"We are counting on your support.","de":"Wir rechnen mit Ihrer Unterstützung.","it":"Contiamo sul vostro sostegno.","es_ar":"Contamos con su apoyo.","fr":"Nous comptons sur votre soutien."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"уточнювати","level":"B1","ru":"уточнять","en":"to clarify","de":"präzisieren","it":"precisare","es_ar":"precisar","fr":"préciser","examples":[{"uk":"Дозвольте уточнити деталі замовлення.","ru":"Позвольте уточнить детали заказа.","en":"Let me clarify the details of the order.","de":"Lassen Sie mich die Einzelheiten der Bestellung präzisieren.","it":"Mi permetta di precisare i dettagli dell'ordine.","es_ar":"Permítame precisar los detalles del pedido.","fr":"Permettez-moi de préciser les détails de la commande."}],"topics":["language-words","abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"роз'яснювати","level":"B1","ru":"разъяснять","en":"to explain","de":"erläutern","it":"chiarire","es_ar":"aclarar","fr":"éclaircir","examples":[{"uk":"Викладач роз'яснює складні правила.","ru":"Преподаватель разъясняет сложные правила.","en":"The lecturer explains the difficult rules.","de":"Der Dozent erläutert die schwierigen Regeln.","it":"Il docente chiarisce le regole difficili.","es_ar":"El profesor aclara las reglas difíciles.","fr":"L'enseignant éclaircit les règles difficiles."}],"topics":["language-words"]},
{"word":"тлумачити","level":"B1","ru":"толковать","en":"to interpret","de":"auslegen","it":"interpretare","es_ar":"interpretar","fr":"interpréter","examples":[{"uk":"Юрист тлумачить положення закону.","ru":"Юрист толкует положения закона.","en":"The lawyer interprets the provisions of the law.","de":"Der Jurist legt die Bestimmungen des Gesetzes aus.","it":"Il giurista interpreta le disposizioni della legge.","es_ar":"El jurista interpreta las disposiciones de la ley.","fr":"Le juriste interprète les dispositions de la loi."}],"topics":["language-words"]},
{"word":"витлумачувати","level":"B1","ru":"истолковывать","en":"to construe","de":"deuten","it":"interpretare","es_ar":"interpretar","fr":"expliquer","examples":[{"uk":"Критики по-різному витлумачують цей роман.","ru":"Критики по-разному истолковывают этот роман.","en":"Critics construe this novel in different ways.","de":"Kritiker deuten diesen Roman unterschiedlich.","it":"I critici interpretano questo romanzo in modi diversi.","es_ar":"Los críticos interpretan esta novela de maneras distintas.","fr":"Les critiques expliquent ce roman de différentes manières."}],"topics":["language-words"]},
{"word":"формулювати","level":"B1","ru":"формулировать","en":"to formulate","de":"formulieren","it":"formulare","es_ar":"formular","fr":"formuler","examples":[{"uk":"Спробуйте формулювати думку чіткіше.","ru":"Попробуйте формулировать мысль чётче.","en":"Try to formulate your idea more clearly.","de":"Versuchen Sie, Ihren Gedanken klarer zu formulieren.","it":"Cerchi di formulare il pensiero più chiaramente.","es_ar":"Intente formular su idea con más claridad.","fr":"Essayez de formuler votre idée plus clairement."}],"topics":["language-words","abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"наголошувати","level":"B1","ru":"подчёркивать","en":"to emphasize","de":"betonen","it":"sottolineare","es_ar":"subrayar","fr":"souligner","examples":[{"uk":"Лектор наголошує на важливості практики.","ru":"Лектор подчёркивает важность практики.","en":"The lecturer emphasizes the importance of practice.","de":"Der Dozent betont die Bedeutung der Praxis.","it":"Il relatore sottolinea l'importanza della pratica.","es_ar":"El conferenciante subraya la importancia de la práctica.","fr":"Le conférencier souligne l'importance de la pratique."}],"topics":["language-words"]},
{"word":"підсумовувати","level":"B1","ru":"подытоживать","en":"to summarize","de":"zusammenfassen","it":"riassumere","es_ar":"resumir","fr":"résumer","examples":[{"uk":"Наприкінці автор підсумовує сказане.","ru":"В конце автор подытоживает сказанное.","en":"At the end, the author summarizes what has been said.","de":"Am Ende fasst der Autor das Gesagte zusammen.","it":"Alla fine l'autore riassume quanto detto.","es_ar":"Al final, el autor resume lo dicho.","fr":"À la fin, l'auteur résume ce qui a été dit."}],"topics":["language-words","abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"узагальнити","level":"B1","ru":"обобщить","en":"to sum up","de":"zusammenfassen","it":"sintetizzare","es_ar":"sintetizar","fr":"synthétiser","examples":[{"uk":"Спробуймо узагальнити результати дослідження.","ru":"Попробуем обобщить результаты исследования.","en":"Let's sum up the results of the study.","de":"Versuchen wir, die Ergebnisse der Studie zusammenzufassen.","it":"Proviamo a sintetizzare i risultati della ricerca.","es_ar":"Intentemos sintetizar los resultados del estudio.","fr":"Essayons de synthétiser les résultats de l'étude."}],"topics":["language-words","abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"поліпшувати","level":"B1","ru":"улучшать","en":"to improve","de":"verbessern","it":"migliorare","es_ar":"mejorar","fr":"améliorer","examples":[{"uk":"Реформа має поліпшувати умови праці.","ru":"Реформа должна улучшать условия труда.","en":"The reform should improve working conditions.","de":"Die Reform soll die Arbeitsbedingungen verbessern.","it":"La riforma deve migliorare le condizioni di lavoro.","es_ar":"La reforma debe mejorar las condiciones laborales.","fr":"La réforme doit améliorer les conditions de travail."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"погіршувати","level":"B1","ru":"ухудшать","en":"to worsen","de":"verschlechtern","it":"peggiorare","es_ar":"empeorar","fr":"aggraver","examples":[{"uk":"Стрес може погіршувати стан здоров'я.","ru":"Стресс может ухудшать состояние здоровья.","en":"Stress can worsen one's health.","de":"Stress kann den Gesundheitszustand verschlechtern.","it":"Lo stress può peggiorare lo stato di salute.","es_ar":"El estrés puede empeorar el estado de salud.","fr":"Le stress peut aggraver l'état de santé."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"уповільнювати","level":"B1","ru":"замедлять","en":"to slow down","de":"verlangsamen","it":"rallentare","es_ar":"ralentizar","fr":"ralentir","examples":[{"uk":"Погана дорога уповільнює рух.","ru":"Плохая дорога замедляет движение.","en":"A bad road slows down traffic.","de":"Eine schlechte Straße verlangsamt den Verkehr.","it":"Una strada dissestata rallenta il traffico.","es_ar":"Una carretera en mal estado ralentiza el tráfico.","fr":"Une mauvaise route ralentit la circulation."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"розширювати","level":"B1","ru":"расширять","en":"to expand","de":"erweitern","it":"ampliare","es_ar":"ampliar","fr":"élargir","examples":[{"uk":"Компанія розширює мережу магазинів.","ru":"Компания расширяет сеть магазинов.","en":"The company is expanding its network of stores.","de":"Das Unternehmen erweitert sein Filialnetz.","it":"L'azienda amplia la rete di negozi.","es_ar":"La empresa amplía su red de tiendas.","fr":"L'entreprise élargit son réseau de magasins."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"звужувати","level":"B1","ru":"сужать","en":"to narrow","de":"verengen","it":"restringere","es_ar":"estrechar","fr":"rétrécir","examples":[{"uk":"Ремонт звужує проїзну частину.","ru":"Ремонт сужает проезжую часть.","en":"The roadworks narrow the carriageway.","de":"Die Bauarbeiten verengen die Fahrbahn.","it":"I lavori restringono la carreggiata.","es_ar":"Las obras estrechan la calzada.","fr":"Les travaux rétrécissent la chaussée."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"зміцнювати","level":"B1","ru":"укреплять","en":"to strengthen","de":"stärken","it":"rafforzare","es_ar":"fortalecer","fr":"renforcer","examples":[{"uk":"Спорт зміцнює здоров'я.","ru":"Спорт укрепляет здоровье.","en":"Sport strengthens health.","de":"Sport stärkt die Gesundheit.","it":"Lo sport rafforza la salute.","es_ar":"El deporte fortalece la salud.","fr":"Le sport renforce la santé."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"послаблювати","level":"B1","ru":"ослаблять","en":"to weaken","de":"schwächen","it":"indebolire","es_ar":"debilitar","fr":"affaiblir","examples":[{"uk":"Недосипання послаблює імунітет.","ru":"Недосыпание ослабляет иммунитет.","en":"Lack of sleep weakens the immune system.","de":"Schlafmangel schwächt das Immunsystem.","it":"La mancanza di sonno indebolisce il sistema immunitario.","es_ar":"La falta de sueño debilita el sistema inmunitario.","fr":"Le manque de sommeil affaiblit le système immunitaire."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"урізноманітнювати","level":"B1","ru":"разнообразить","en":"to diversify","de":"variieren","it":"diversificare","es_ar":"variar","fr":"diversifier","examples":[{"uk":"Кухар прагне урізноманітнювати меню.","ru":"Повар стремится разнообразить меню.","en":"The cook strives to diversify the menu.","de":"Der Koch bemüht sich, das Menü abwechslungsreicher zu gestalten.","it":"Il cuoco cerca di diversificare il menù.","es_ar":"El cocinero procura variar el menú.","fr":"Le cuisinier cherche à diversifier le menu."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"чергувати","level":"B1","ru":"чередовать","en":"to alternate","de":"abwechseln","it":"alternare","es_ar":"alternar","fr":"alterner","examples":[{"uk":"Корисно чергувати роботу й відпочинок.","ru":"Полезно чередовать работу и отдых.","en":"It is useful to alternate work and rest.","de":"Es ist nützlich, Arbeit und Erholung abzuwechseln.","it":"È utile alternare lavoro e riposo.","es_ar":"Es útil alternar el trabajo y el descanso.","fr":"Il est utile d'alterner le travail et le repos."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"поновлювати","level":"B1","ru":"возобновлять","en":"to renew","de":"erneuern","it":"rinnovare","es_ar":"renovar","fr":"renouveler","examples":[{"uk":"Треба вчасно поновлювати передплату.","ru":"Нужно вовремя возобновлять подписку.","en":"You need to renew your subscription on time.","de":"Man muss das Abonnement rechtzeitig erneuern.","it":"Bisogna rinnovare l'abbonamento in tempo.","es_ar":"Hay que renovar la suscripción a tiempo.","fr":"Il faut renouveler l'abonnement à temps."}],"topics":["abstract-ideas"]},
{"word":"злива","level":"B1","ru":"ливень","en":"downpour","de":"der Platzregen","it":"l'acquazzone","es_ar":"el aguacero","fr":"l'averse","examples":[{"uk":"Раптова злива застала нас без парасольок.","ru":"Внезапный ливень застал нас без зонтов.","en":"The sudden downpour caught us without umbrellas.","de":"Der plötzliche Platzregen erwischte uns ohne Regenschirme.","it":"L'improvviso acquazzone ci ha sorpresi senza ombrelli.","es_ar":"El aguacero repentino nos agarró sin paraguas.","fr":"L'averse soudaine nous a surpris sans parapluie."}],"topics":["weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"град","level":"B1","ru":"град","en":"hail","de":"der Hagel","it":"la grandine","es_ar":"el granizo","fr":"la grêle","examples":[{"uk":"Град побив усі помідори на городі.","ru":"Град побил все помидоры в огороде.","en":"The hail destroyed all the tomatoes in the garden.","de":"Der Hagel hat alle Tomaten im Garten zerschlagen.","it":"La grandine ha rovinato tutti i pomodori nell'orto.","es_ar":"El granizo arruinó todos los tomates de la huerta.","fr":"La grêle a détruit toutes les tomates du potager."}],"topics":["weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"ожеледь","level":"B1","ru":"гололёд","en":"black ice","de":"das Glatteis","it":"il ghiaccio nero","es_ar":"el hielo negro","fr":"le verglas","examples":[{"uk":"Через ожеледь на дорогах сталося кілька аварій.","ru":"Из-за гололёда на дорогах произошло несколько аварий.","en":"Because of the black ice on the roads, several accidents happened.","de":"Wegen des Glatteises auf den Straßen gab es mehrere Unfälle.","it":"A causa del ghiaccio nero sulle strade sono avvenuti diversi incidenti.","es_ar":"Por el hielo negro en las rutas ocurrieron varios accidentes.","fr":"À cause du verglas sur les routes, plusieurs accidents sont arrivés."}],"topics":["weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"роса","level":"B1","ru":"роса","en":"dew","de":"der Tau","it":"la rugiada","es_ar":"el rocío","fr":"la rosée","examples":[{"uk":"Уранці трава була вкрита росою.","ru":"Утром трава была покрыта росой.","en":"In the morning the grass was covered with dew.","de":"Am Morgen war das Gras mit Tau bedeckt.","it":"Al mattino l'erba era coperta di rugiada.","es_ar":"Por la mañana el pasto estaba cubierto de rocío.","fr":"Le matin, l'herbe était couverte de rosée."}],"topics":["weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"іній","level":"B1","ru":"иней","en":"hoarfrost","de":"der Raureif","it":"la brina","es_ar":"la escarcha","fr":"le givre","examples":[{"uk":"Дерева вкрилися білим інеєм.","ru":"Деревья покрылись белым инеем.","en":"The trees were covered with white hoarfrost.","de":"Die Bäume waren mit weißem Raureif bedeckt.","it":"Gli alberi si sono coperti di brina bianca.","es_ar":"Los árboles se cubrieron de escarcha blanca.","fr":"Les arbres se sont couverts de givre blanc."}],"topics":["weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"грім","level":"B1","ru":"гром","en":"thunder","de":"der Donner","it":"il tuono","es_ar":"el trueno","fr":"le tonnerre","examples":[{"uk":"Гуркіт грому налякав маленьку дитину.","ru":"Раскат грома напугал маленького ребёнка.","en":"The clap of thunder frightened the little child.","de":"Der Donnerschlag erschreckte das kleine Kind.","it":"Il rombo del tuono ha spaventato il bambino piccolo.","es_ar":"El estruendo del trueno asustó al niño pequeño.","fr":"Le coup de tonnerre a effrayé le petit enfant."}],"topics":["weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"замет","level":"B1","ru":"сугроб","en":"snowdrift","de":"die Schneewehe","it":"il cumulo di neve","es_ar":"el ventisquero","fr":"la congère","examples":[{"uk":"За ніч вітер намів великий замет під дверима.","ru":"За ночь ветер намёл большой сугроб у двери.","en":"Overnight the wind piled up a big snowdrift by the door.","de":"Über Nacht türmte der Wind eine große Schneewehe vor der Tür auf.","it":"Durante la notte il vento ha ammassato un grande cumulo di neve davanti alla porta.","es_ar":"Durante la noche el viento amontonó un gran ventisquero junto a la puerta.","fr":"Pendant la nuit, le vent a formé une grande congère devant la porte."}],"topics":["weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"хуртовина","level":"B1","ru":"метель","en":"snowstorm","de":"der Schneesturm","it":"la bufera di neve","es_ar":"la tormenta de nieve","fr":"la tempête de neige","examples":[{"uk":"Через хуртовину закрили всі гірські дороги.","ru":"Из-за метели закрыли все горные дороги.","en":"Because of the snowstorm all the mountain roads were closed.","de":"Wegen des Schneesturms wurden alle Bergstraßen gesperrt.","it":"A causa della bufera di neve hanno chiuso tutte le strade di montagna.","es_ar":"Por la tormenta de nieve cerraron todos los caminos de montaña.","fr":"À cause de la tempête de neige, toutes les routes de montagne ont été fermées."}],"topics":["weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"спека","level":"B1","ru":"жара","en":"heat","de":"die Hitze","it":"il caldo","es_ar":"el calor","fr":"la chaleur","examples":[{"uk":"Улітку тут стоїть нестерпна спека.","ru":"Летом здесь стоит невыносимая жара.","en":"In summer there is unbearable heat here.","de":"Im Sommer herrscht hier unerträgliche Hitze.","it":"In estate qui fa un caldo insopportabile.","es_ar":"En verano acá hace un calor insoportable.","fr":"En été, il fait ici une chaleur insupportable."}],"topics":["weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"зсув","level":"B1","ru":"оползень","en":"landslide","de":"der Erdrutsch","it":"la frana","es_ar":"el deslizamiento de tierra","fr":"le glissement de terrain","examples":[{"uk":"Після зливи стався зсув, що перекрив трасу.","ru":"После ливня произошёл оползень, который перекрыл трассу.","en":"After the downpour a landslide occurred and blocked the highway.","de":"Nach dem Platzregen kam es zu einem Erdrutsch, der die Straße blockierte.","it":"Dopo l'acquazzone si è verificata una frana che ha bloccato la strada.","es_ar":"Después del aguacero hubo un deslizamiento de tierra que cortó la ruta.","fr":"Après l'averse, un glissement de terrain a bloqué la route."}],"topics":["nature-environment","military-safety"]},
{"word":"буревій","level":"B1","ru":"ураган","en":"gale","de":"der Orkan","it":"l'uragano","es_ar":"el vendaval","fr":"l'ouragan","examples":[{"uk":"Нічний буревій повалив кілька старих дерев.","ru":"Ночной ураган повалил несколько старых деревьев.","en":"The night gale knocked down several old trees.","de":"Der nächtliche Orkan riss mehrere alte Bäume um.","it":"L'uragano notturno ha abbattuto diversi alberi vecchi.","es_ar":"El vendaval nocturno derribó varios árboles viejos.","fr":"L'ouragan nocturne a abattu plusieurs vieux arbres."}],"topics":["weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"протяг","level":"B1","ru":"сквозняк","en":"draught","de":"der Luftzug","it":"la corrente d'aria","es_ar":"la corriente de aire","fr":"le courant d'air","examples":[{"uk":"Зачини вікно, бо через протяг можна застудитися.","ru":"Закрой окно, а то из-за сквозняка можно простудиться.","en":"Close the window, because you can catch a cold from the draught.","de":"Mach das Fenster zu, denn durch den Luftzug kann man sich erkälten.","it":"Chiudi la finestra, perché con la corrente d'aria ci si può raffreddare.","es_ar":"Cerrá la ventana, porque con la corriente de aire uno se puede resfriar.","fr":"Ferme la fenêtre, car on peut attraper froid à cause du courant d'air."}],"topics":["weather-seasons","home"]},
{"word":"відлига","level":"B1","ru":"оттепель","en":"thaw","de":"das Tauwetter","it":"il disgelo","es_ar":"el deshielo","fr":"le dégel","examples":[{"uk":"Після морозів настала несподівана відлига.","ru":"После морозов наступила неожиданная оттепель.","en":"After the frosts an unexpected thaw set in.","de":"Nach dem Frost setzte ein unerwartetes Tauwetter ein.","it":"Dopo le gelate è arrivato un disgelo inaspettato.","es_ar":"Después de las heladas llegó un deshielo inesperado.","fr":"Après les gelées, un dégel inattendu s'est installé."}],"topics":["weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"паморозь","level":"B1","ru":"изморозь","en":"rime","de":"der Reif","it":"la galaverna","es_ar":"la cencellada","fr":"le givre blanc","examples":[{"uk":"На гілках блищала тонка паморозь.","ru":"На ветках блестела тонкая изморозь.","en":"A thin layer of rime glittered on the branches.","de":"Auf den Ästen glitzerte ein dünner Reif.","it":"Sui rami brillava una sottile galaverna.","es_ar":"En las ramas brillaba una fina cencellada.","fr":"Sur les branches scintillait un fin givre blanc."}],"topics":["weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"мряка","level":"B1","ru":"морось","en":"drizzle","de":"der Nieselregen","it":"la pioggerella","es_ar":"la llovizna","fr":"la bruine","examples":[{"uk":"Цілий день надворі сіяла дрібна мряка.","ru":"Целый день на улице моросила мелкая морось.","en":"All day a fine drizzle fell outside.","de":"Den ganzen Tag fiel draußen feiner Nieselregen.","it":"Tutto il giorno fuori cadeva una sottile pioggerella.","es_ar":"Todo el día afuera caía una fina llovizna.","fr":"Toute la journée, une fine bruine tombait dehors."}],"topics":["weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"заметіль","level":"B1","ru":"вьюга","en":"blizzard","de":"das Schneegestöber","it":"la tormenta","es_ar":"la nevisca","fr":"le blizzard","examples":[{"uk":"У полі заметіль замела всі стежки.","ru":"В поле вьюга замела все тропинки.","en":"In the field the blizzard covered all the paths.","de":"Auf dem Feld verwehte das Schneegestöber alle Pfade.","it":"Nel campo la tormenta ha coperto tutti i sentieri.","es_ar":"En el campo la nevisca tapó todos los senderos.","fr":"Dans le champ, le blizzard a recouvert tous les sentiers."}],"topics":["weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"смерч","level":"B1","ru":"смерч","en":"tornado","de":"der Tornado","it":"il tornado","es_ar":"el tornado","fr":"la tornade","examples":[{"uk":"Над морем утворився небезпечний смерч.","ru":"Над морем образовался опасный смерч.","en":"A dangerous tornado formed over the sea.","de":"Über dem Meer bildete sich ein gefährlicher Tornado.","it":"Sopra il mare si è formato un pericoloso tornado.","es_ar":"Sobre el mar se formó un peligroso tornado.","fr":"Une tornade dangereuse s'est formée au-dessus de la mer."}],"topics":["weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"землетрус","level":"B1","ru":"землетрясение","en":"earthquake","de":"das Erdbeben","it":"il terremoto","es_ar":"el terremoto","fr":"le tremblement de terre","examples":[{"uk":"Уночі стався потужний землетрус.","ru":"Ночью произошло мощное землетрясение.","en":"A powerful earthquake happened during the night.","de":"In der Nacht ereignete sich ein starkes Erdbeben.","it":"Di notte è avvenuto un forte terremoto.","es_ar":"Durante la noche ocurrió un potente terremoto.","fr":"Un puissant tremblement de terre s'est produit pendant la nuit."}],"topics":["nature-environment","military-safety"]},
{"word":"виверження","level":"B1","ru":"извержение","en":"eruption","de":"der Ausbruch","it":"l'eruzione","es_ar":"la erupción","fr":"l'éruption","examples":[{"uk":"Виверження вулкана вкрило місто попелом.","ru":"Извержение вулкана покрыло город пеплом.","en":"The volcanic eruption covered the city with ash.","de":"Der Vulkanausbruch bedeckte die Stadt mit Asche.","it":"L'eruzione del vulcano ha coperto la città di cenere.","es_ar":"La erupción del volcán cubrió la ciudad de ceniza.","fr":"L'éruption du volcan a recouvert la ville de cendres."}],"topics":["nature-environment","military-safety"]},
{"word":"лавина","level":"B1","ru":"лавина","en":"avalanche","de":"die Lawine","it":"la valanga","es_ar":"la avalancha","fr":"l'avalanche","examples":[{"uk":"У горах сходить лавина, тому туди небезпечно йти.","ru":"В горах сходит лавина, поэтому туда опасно идти.","en":"An avalanche is coming down in the mountains, so it is dangerous to go there.","de":"In den Bergen geht eine Lawine ab, deshalb ist es gefährlich, dorthin zu gehen.","it":"In montagna scende una valanga, perciò è pericoloso andarci.","es_ar":"En la montaña baja una avalancha, por eso es peligroso ir ahí.","fr":"Une avalanche descend dans les montagnes, il est donc dangereux d'y aller."}],"topics":["weather-seasons","military-safety"]},
{"word":"приплив","level":"B1","ru":"прилив","en":"high tide","de":"die Flut","it":"l'alta marea","es_ar":"la marea alta","fr":"la marée haute","examples":[{"uk":"Під час припливу вода піднімається до самих скель.","ru":"Во время прилива вода поднимается до самых скал.","en":"During high tide the water rises right up to the rocks.","de":"Bei Flut steigt das Wasser bis an die Felsen.","it":"Durante l'alta marea l'acqua sale fino agli scogli.","es_ar":"Durante la marea alta el agua sube hasta las rocas.","fr":"À marée haute, l'eau monte jusqu'aux rochers."}],"topics":["nature-environment","geography"]},
{"word":"відплив","level":"B1","ru":"отлив","en":"low tide","de":"die Ebbe","it":"la bassa marea","es_ar":"la marea baja","fr":"la marée basse","examples":[{"uk":"Під час відпливу на піску залишаються мушлі.","ru":"Во время отлива на песке остаются ракушки.","en":"During low tide shells are left on the sand.","de":"Bei Ebbe bleiben Muscheln auf dem Sand zurück.","it":"Durante la bassa marea sulla sabbia restano le conchiglie.","es_ar":"Durante la marea baja quedan caracoles sobre la arena.","fr":"À marée basse, des coquillages restent sur le sable."}],"topics":["nature-environment","geography"]},
{"word":"штиль","level":"B1","ru":"штиль","en":"calm","de":"die Windstille","it":"la bonaccia","es_ar":"la calma chicha","fr":"le calme plat","examples":[{"uk":"На морі був повний штиль, і вітрила обвисли.","ru":"На море был полный штиль, и паруса обвисли.","en":"There was a complete calm at sea, and the sails hung limp.","de":"Auf dem Meer herrschte völlige Windstille, und die Segel hingen schlaff.","it":"Sul mare c'era una bonaccia completa e le vele pendevano molli.","es_ar":"En el mar había una calma chicha total y las velas colgaban flojas.","fr":"Il y avait un calme plat sur la mer, et les voiles pendaient mollement."}],"topics":["weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"шторм","level":"B1","ru":"шторм","en":"storm","de":"der Sturm","it":"la tempesta","es_ar":"la tormenta","fr":"la tempête","examples":[{"uk":"Через шторм усі кораблі залишилися в порту.","ru":"Из-за шторма все корабли остались в порту.","en":"Because of the storm all the ships stayed in port.","de":"Wegen des Sturms blieben alle Schiffe im Hafen.","it":"A causa della tempesta tutte le navi sono rimaste in porto.","es_ar":"Por la tormenta todos los barcos quedaron en el puerto.","fr":"À cause de la tempête, tous les navires sont restés au port."}],"topics":["weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"спалах","level":"B1","ru":"вспышка","en":"flash","de":"der Blitzstrahl","it":"il lampo","es_ar":"el destello","fr":"l'éclat","examples":[{"uk":"Яскравий спалах блискавки засліпив на мить.","ru":"Яркая вспышка молнии на миг ослепила.","en":"A bright flash of lightning blinded us for a moment.","de":"Ein heller Blitzstrahl blendete uns für einen Moment.","it":"Un lampo luminoso ci ha accecato per un istante.","es_ar":"Un destello brillante del relámpago nos cegó por un instante.","fr":"Un éclat vif de la foudre nous a aveuglés un instant."}],"topics":["weather-seasons","physics"]},
{"word":"порив вітру","level":"B1","ru":"порыв ветра","en":"gust of wind","de":"die Windböe","it":"la raffica di vento","es_ar":"la ráfaga de viento","fr":"la rafale de vent","examples":[{"uk":"Раптовий порив вітру зірвав з мене капелюх.","ru":"Внезапный порыв ветра сорвал с меня шляпу.","en":"A sudden gust of wind blew my hat off.","de":"Eine plötzliche Windböe riss mir den Hut vom Kopf.","it":"Un'improvvisa raffica di vento mi ha strappato il cappello.","es_ar":"Una ráfaga de viento repentina me voló el sombrero.","fr":"Une rafale de vent soudaine m'a arraché le chapeau."}],"topics":["weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"атмосферний тиск","level":"B1","ru":"атмосферное давление","en":"atmospheric pressure","de":"der Luftdruck","it":"la pressione atmosferica","es_ar":"la presión atmosférica","fr":"la pression atmosphérique","examples":[{"uk":"При низькому атмосферному тиску в мене болить голова.","ru":"При низком атмосферном давлении у меня болит голова.","en":"When the atmospheric pressure is low, I get a headache.","de":"Bei niedrigem Luftdruck bekomme ich Kopfschmerzen.","it":"Con la pressione atmosferica bassa mi viene mal di testa.","es_ar":"Con la presión atmosférica baja me duele la cabeza.","fr":"Quand la pression atmosphérique est basse, j'ai mal à la tête."}],"topics":["weather-seasons","physics"]},
{"word":"вологість","level":"B1","ru":"влажность","en":"humidity","de":"die Luftfeuchtigkeit","it":"l'umidità","es_ar":"la humedad","fr":"l'humidité","examples":[{"uk":"Улітку висока вологість погано переноситься.","ru":"Летом высокая влажность плохо переносится.","en":"In summer the high humidity is hard to bear.","de":"Im Sommer ist die hohe Luftfeuchtigkeit schwer zu ertragen.","it":"In estate l'alta umidità si sopporta male.","es_ar":"En verano la humedad alta se soporta mal.","fr":"En été, l'humidité élevée est difficile à supporter."}],"topics":["weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"прогноз","level":"B1","ru":"прогноз","en":"forecast","de":"die Vorhersage","it":"le previsioni","es_ar":"el pronóstico","fr":"les prévisions","examples":[{"uk":"Прогноз погоди обіцяє дощ на вихідні.","ru":"Прогноз погоды обещает дождь на выходные.","en":"The weather forecast promises rain for the weekend.","de":"Die Wettervorhersage verspricht Regen fürs Wochenende.","it":"Le previsioni del tempo prevedono pioggia per il fine settimana.","es_ar":"El pronóstico del tiempo anuncia lluvia para el fin de semana.","fr":"Les prévisions météo annoncent de la pluie pour le week-end."}],"topics":["weather-seasons"]},
{"word":"опади","level":"B1","ru":"осадки","en":"precipitation","de":"der Niederschlag","it":"le precipitazioni","es_ar":"las precipitaciones","fr":"les précipitations","examples":[{"uk":"Синоптики прогнозують сильні опади вдень.","ru":"Синоптики прогнозируют сильные осадки днём.","en":"Meteorologists forecast heavy precipitation during the day.","de":"Die Meteorologen sagen starken Niederschlag für den Tag voraus.","it":"I meteorologi prevedono forti precipitazioni durante il giorno.","es_ar":"Los meteorólogos pronostican fuertes precipitaciones durante el día.","fr":"Les météorologues prévoient de fortes précipitations dans la journée."}],"topics":["weather-seasons"]}
